    <note type="biography">
        <p>Oratorio and operatic prima donna. Sang at the Birmingham Music Festival, 1837, before undertaking a European tour, 1838–43. She returned to England in 1851 where she gave regular performances and sang at the opening of the re-erected Crystal Palace in 1854.</p></note>
